---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="about — ii4ki"
  description="What I work on, what I write about, and how to reach me."
  path="about"
  pathMeta="cat me.md"
  activeNav="about"
>
  <section class="about-section">
    <h2>what I do</h2>
    <p>I build small, focused tools that solve problems I keep running into. Most of them are personal automation: bash scripts, AI-assisted pipelines, a statusline here, a secrets layer there. None of them are products. All of them save me time every day. The master plan is to eventually weave them together.</p>
    <p>My current obsession is figuring out which parts of my workflow can be handed to an agent without losing the things I actually enjoy about software.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="about-section">
    <h2>what I write about</h2>
    <p>bash, secrets, Claude Code, agent workflows, ops. Practical posts about the boring scaffolding that makes the interesting work possible.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="about-section">
    <h2>stack</h2>
    <article class="project-card" style="margin-top:8px">
      <div class="head">
        <span class="name">current-stack</span>
        <span class="tag-bracket live">[LIVE]</span>
      </div>
      <div class="links">
        <div><span class="branch">├──</span> <span class="k">languages</span>&nbsp; <span style="color:var(--text)">bash, python, typescript</span></div>
        <div><span class="branch">├──</span> <span class="k">tools</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style="color:var(--text)">claude code, opencode, git</span></div>
        <div><span class="branch">└──</span> <span class="k">infra</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style="color:var(--text)">github actions, github pages, vercel, cloudflare</span></div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="about-section">
    <h2>contact</h2>
    <article class="project-card" style="margin-top:8px">
      <div class="head">
        <span class="name">reach-me</span>
        <span class="tag-bracket live">[LIVE]</span>
      </div>
      <div class="links">
        <div><span class="branch">├──</span> <span class="k">github</span>&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href="https://github.com/bitcoin21ideas" rel="noopener">github.com/bitcoin21ideas</a></div>
        <div><span class="branch">├──</span> <span class="k">rss</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href="/rss.xml">/rss.xml</a></div>
        <div><span class="branch">└──</span> <span class="k">email</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href="mailto:tony@loom.ge">tony@loom.ge</a></div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </section>
</Base>
